---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Calendar, Clock, Globe, Headphones, Menu } from 'lucide-react';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#FAF8F5]">
    {/* Header */}
    <header class="border-b border-[#E5E0D8] bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm sticky top-0 z-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16 sm:h-20">
          <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <img
              src="/images/jizo.jpg"
              alt="Jizo Bodhisattva - Core Self Reiki Logo"
              class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 object-contain"
            />
            <span class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl text-[#2C1810]">Core Self Reiki</span>
          </a>

          {/* Desktop Navigation */}
          <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
            <a href="#home" class="text-[#4A4A4A] hover:text-[#7C3F47] transition-colors text-sm">
              Home
            </a>
            <a href="#reiki-ryoho" class="text-[#4A4A4A] hover:text-[#7C3F47] transition-colors text-sm">
              Reiki Ryoho
            </a>
            <a href="#sessions" class="text-[#4A4A4A] hover:text-[#7C3F47] transition-colors text-sm">
              Reiki Sessions
            </a>
            <a href="#courses" class="text-[#4A4A4A] hover:text-[#7C3F47] transition-colors text-sm">
              Courses
            </a>
            <a href="#contact" class="text-[#4A4A4A] hover:text-[#7C3F47] transition-colors text-sm">
              Contact
            </a>
          </nav>

          {/* Mobile Menu Button */}
          <button class="md:hidden p-2">
            <Menu className="w-6 h-6 text-[#4A4A4A]" />
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="relative w-full h-[45vh] sm:h-[55vh] max-h-[480px] overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="/images/flora-warm-bg.jpeg"
        alt="Core Self Reiki - Warm Floral Background"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/10 to-transparent"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-10 sm:py-12 bg-[#F5F1EB]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl text-center">
        <blockquote class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-[#2C1810] mb-4 text-balance italic">
          "The way to do is to be."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#5A5A5A] mb-6">(Lao-Tzu)</p>
        <blockquote class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl text-[#2C1810] text-balance italic">
          "People should not consider so much what they are to do, as what they are."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#5A5A5A]">(Meister Eckhart)</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="home" class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
            Our core self is our essence, our still silent center of consciousness in the ocean of oneness. Referred
            to as true nature, original nature, or inner luminosity, this deeper reality of the self is experienced as
            a simple awake presence or pure being which manifests explicitly as love, kindness, peace, joy, truth,
            wisdom, and freedom…
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
            When rooted in our core self, we feel at home in the world and in ourselves; our lives become effortless
            and authentic, clear expressions of who and what we truly are, unfolding in the realm of synchronicity
            rather than causality; we live openly, correctly, and fully, we love well and deeply, and we have a sense
            of connection, contentment, and joy, of sacred meaning and value.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">
            The purpose of Core Self Reiki.ca is to encourage individuals to discover, reclaim, deepen, and integrate
            their experience of their core self through the practice of Reiki Ryoho.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Our logo, created by artist Yosei Kansaku of Japan, reflects this aim. It represents Jizo, a bodhisattva
            who goes fearlessly wherever his help is needed by those on the path to enlightenment. His qualities are
            benevolence, determination, and unflagging optimism. His message might translate from Japanese as:{" "}
            <span class="font-serif italic">
              "Put your mind at ease and trust yourself; your presence itself is light and love."
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-[#F5F1EB]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl text-center">
        <p class="text-lg text-[#5A5A5A] mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          To find out more about{" "}
          <a href="#reiki-ryoho" class="text-[#7C3F47] hover:underline font-medium">
            Reiki Ryoho
          </a>
          , to book a{" "}
          <a href="#sessions" class="text-[#7C3F47] hover:underline font-medium">
            Reiki session
          </a>
          , or to sign up for a{" "}
          <a href="#courses" class="text-[#7C3F47] hover:underline font-medium">
            course
          </a>
          , please{" "}
          <a href="#contact" class="text-[#7C3F47] hover:underline font-medium">
            contact
          </a>{" "}
          Elyssa Matthews.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button size="lg" class="bg-[#7C3F47] hover:bg-[#6A3540] text-white text-base px-8">
            Book a Session
          </Button>
          <Button
            size="lg"
            variant="outline"
            class="border-[#7C3F47] text-[#7C3F47] hover:bg-[#7C3F47]/5 text-base px-8 bg-transparent"
          >
            Learn About Courses
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Information Cards with Icons */}
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          {/* Card 1 */}
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#D4A574]/20 mb-4">
              <Calendar className="w-8 h-8 text-[#D4A574]" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-[#2C1810] mb-2">Flexible Scheduling</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed">
              Choose times that work best for your personal healing journey
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* Card 2 */}
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#D4A574]/20 mb-4">
              <Clock className="w-8 h-8 text-[#D4A574]" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-[#2C1810] mb-2">Personalized Sessions</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed">
              Each session is tailored to your unique needs and spiritual journey
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* Card 3 */}
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#D4A574]/20 mb-4">
              <Globe className="w-8 h-8 text-[#D4A574]" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-[#2C1810] mb-2">Distance Reiki Available</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed">
              Experience healing energy from anywhere in the world
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* Card 4 */}
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#D4A574]/20 mb-4">
              <Headphones className="w-8 h-8 text-[#D4A574]" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-[#2C1810] mb-2">Experienced Guidance</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed">
              Learn from a dedicated practitioner committed to your growth
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Services Preview */}
    <section id="reiki-ryoho" class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-[#F5F1EB]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-[#2C1810] text-center mb-12">
          Explore Reiki Ryoho
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          {/* Service 1 */}
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#2C1810] mb-4">Reiki Sessions</h3>
            <p class="text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Experience personalized healing sessions that help you reconnect with your core self through the
              traditional practice of Reiki Ryoho.
            </p>
            <Button
              variant="outline"
              class="border-[#7C3F47] text-[#7C3F47] hover:bg-[#7C3F47]/5 w-full bg-transparent"
            >
              Learn More
            </Button>
          </div>

          {/* Service 2 */}
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#2C1810] mb-4">Reiki Courses</h3>
            <p class="text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Deepen your understanding and practice of Reiki through comprehensive courses designed for all levels of
              experience.
            </p>
            <Button
              variant="outline"
              class="border-[#7C3F47] text-[#7C3F47] hover:bg-[#7C3F47]/5 w-full bg-transparent"
            >
              View Courses
            </Button>
          </div>

          {/* Service 3 */}
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-[#2C1810] mb-4">About Reiki Ryoho</h3>
            <p class="text-[#5A5A5A] leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Discover the history, principles, and practice of Reiki Ryoho and how it can support your spiritual
              journey.
            </p>
            <Button
              variant="outline"
              class="border-[#7C3F47] text-[#7C3F47] hover:bg-[#7C3F47]/5 w-full bg-transparent"
            >
              Read More
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* CTA Section */}
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-[#7C3F47] text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6 text-balance">
          Begin Your Journey to Your Core Self
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-8 opacity-90 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-pretty">
          Discover the peace, wisdom, and authentic presence that lies at the heart of who you truly are.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button size="lg" class="bg-white text-[#7C3F47] hover:bg-white/90 text-base px-8">
            Contact Elyssa Matthews
          </Button>
          <Button
            size="lg"
            variant="outline"
            class="border-white text-white hover:bg-white/10 text-base px-8 bg-transparent"
          >
            Learn More
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Footer */}
    <footer class="bg-[#2C1810] text-white py-12">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <img src="/images/jizo.jpg" alt="Jizo Bodhisattva" class="w-10 h-10 object-contain" />
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl">Core Self Reiki</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
              Discover, reclaim, deepen, and integrate your experience of your core self through Reiki Ryoho.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Quick Links</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>
                <a href="#home" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  Home
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#reiki-ryoho" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  Reiki Ryoho
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#sessions" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  Reiki Sessions
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#courses" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  Courses
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#contact" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                  Contact
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4">Connect</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mb-4">
              For inquiries about sessions or courses, please contact Elyssa Matthews.
            </p>
            <Button size="sm" class="bg-[#7C3F47] hover:bg-[#6A3540] text-white">
              Get in Touch
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 text-center text-sm text-white/50">
          <p>&copy; 2025 Core Self Reiki. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs">Logo artwork by Yosei Kansaku</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>